OL,3,CITV's Ruth Dodsworth receives OBE for
OL,4,Cservices to domestic abuse survivors
OL,6,FITV Cymru Wales weather presenter Ruth
OL,7,FDodsworth has received an OBE (Order
OL,8,Fof the British Empire) from the King
OL,9,Ffor services to survivors of domestic
OL,10,Fabuse.
OL,12,FKing Charles presented her with the
OL,13,Fhonour at an investiture ceremony at
OL,14,FWindsor Castle on Tuesday, 9 December.
