OL,3,CITV's Ruth Dodsworth receives OBE for
OL,4,Cservices to domestic abuse survivors
OL,6,FSpeaking after being awarded the
OL,7,Fhonour in the King's Birthday Honours
OL,8,Flist, Ruth said: "It feels all a bit
OL,9,Fsurreal and completely unbelievable,
OL,10,Fand I'm over the moon. It's just the
OL,11,Fbiggest honour I think I have ever had
OL,12,Fin my entire life.
OL,14,F"This is not just for me this is for
OL,15,Fmy family, my friends and everybody
OL,16,Fwho has been on this very strange
OL,17,Fjourney that I've been on, everybody
OL,18,Fwho has supported me.
