OL,3,CITV's Ruth Dodsworth receives OBE for
OL,4,Cservices to domestic abuse survivors
OL,6,F"And this is for everybody who is
OL,7,Fgoing on journeys of their own as well
OL,8,Fbecause it's not easy and domestic
OL,9,Fabuse is out there and it's everywhere.
OL,11,F"That's why this honour is also so
OL,12,Fimportant because it allows me to keep
OL,13,Fthat conversation going. I'm going to
OL,14,Fuse it wisely and then hopefully one
OL,15,Fday we won't have to talk about
OL,16,Fdomestic abuse because it won't be an
OL,17,Fissue anymore.
OL,19,F"But until that point, this honour is
OL,20,Ffor everybody who has been affected by
OL,21,Fdomestic abuse and I'm just so proud."
