OL,3,CITV's Ruth Dodsworth receives OBE for
OL,4,Cservices to domestic abuse survivors
OL,6,FThe broadcaster endured almost a
OL,7,Fdecade of coercive control from her ex-
OL,8,Fhusband, who was jailed in 2021 for
OL,9,Fthree years for stalking and coercive
OL,10,Fcontrol.
OL,12,FRuth has since become a vocal
OL,13,Fcampaigner for domestic abuse
OL,14,Fsurvivors, working closely with
OL,15,Fseveral domestic abuse charities to
OL,16,Fencourage other survivors to come
OL,17,Fforward.
